                     ClassLoader classLoader,
                     JavaModule module,
                     boolean loaded)
        Creates a new unresolved resolution.
        参数:
        typeDescription - The type that is not transformed.
        classLoader - The unresolved type's class loader.
        module - The non-transformed type's module or null if the current VM does not support modules.
        loaded - true if the type is already loaded.
